	OUT_SOURCE_PATH SOURCE_PATH
	REPO RealTimeChris/DiscordCoreAPI
	REF e9548806ffda7e00ee080543bcb8a18a166ac443
	SHA512 989bfc9569a11803d47ae2acd0e2e772a050396725d2ac640d04f5a1558b206cad7246cbb1d1fa79b47105a0b0d20da8d8f3e8b8d5d00716d257dbc635becb70
